on.project_id}}/milestones/{{$json.milestone_id}}\" target=\"_blank\">\n          View Milestone Details\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n\n  </table>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n    Kindly review the updated milestone details and adjust plans, dependencies, and resources accordingly.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Regards,<br>\n    <strong>Project Controls Team</strong>\n  </p>\n\n</div>",
